 The world has fallen into crisis. All the lands have sunk, a deadly infection 
 is spreading through the population, and no one can produce enough food for 
 humanity to survive. The only hope lies in Metafalcia, a green utopia which can 
 only be raised through Song Magic. However, the Goddess in charge of Song Magic 
 will not allow humanity to realize their dream of a perfect world. The leader 
 of the world creates a government against the Goddess, and is wildly backed by 
 the people. Explore a vast and deep world as Croix, a soldier from the 
 exclusive main city, and help to save the world and find the utopia of
